values:
Nothing has changed too much in the past month or so.&nbsp; I have moved into my grandfathers house. 
Yeah, it's weird.&nbsp; 

The house is really a dream though right now. I couldn't ask for more.&nbsp; 


I really have realized i need to start cleaning up a bit. 
You never know the stink you get yourself into until you're knee deep. 
 Looking at what preventative steps i have taken to begin that path tonight makes the task at hand seems futile. 


We'll see.&nbsp; 

The cycle never stops, ends, or in many begging pleads, at least slows down.
